  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/3391457710b23c54d4e98369a128ff86.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/3391457710b23c54d4e98369a128ff86.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/3391457710b23c54d4e98369a128ff86.mp4?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll Five is a dice-based <strong>roguelike</strong> deckbuilder that challenges you to master the art of <strong>dice rolling</strong> and deal shocking amount of <strong>damage</strong> to monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/1d35548f76dfee80c8e7c372f16d5ad3.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/1d35548f76dfee80c8e7c372f16d5ad3.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/1d35548f76dfee80c8e7c372f16d5ad3.mp4?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/b0067554ade81fb083e5525bf1242aad.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=620 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/b0067554ade81fb083e5525bf1242aad.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/1ab94bd475e1035b1544074dbb6b6211.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=800 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/1ab94bd475e1035b1544074dbb6b6211.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your dice <strong>figure</strong> attacks with unique prisms to craft innovative strategies. Deal massive damage to defeat enemies and <strong>unlock</strong> secret decks through original gameplay. Defeat the final boss to free <strong>Fortuna</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/74fd9e593250f16688a4c157890c8489.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=755 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/74fd9e593250f16688a4c157890c8489.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/16469c47e376cfbb1a96d0a277ce438e.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=295 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/16469c47e376cfbb1a96d0a277ce438e.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fast-paced and immersive dice-rolling adventure. A game that combines the thrill of dice rolling with <strong>deep</strong> strategic gameplay. Each deck offers an escalading <strong>challenge</strong> with 4 levels of difficulty, and every run is seeded for an <strong>endless and shareable </strong>experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command your <strong>devastating arsenal</strong> of Decks, Prisms, Runes, Omega, Potions, and Relics. Combine them with skill to transform your dice figures into fiery <strong>forces</strong> of destruction.  <br>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >165+ Prisms, each with its own ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70+ Relics to provide permanent boosts and enhance your attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22+ Decks offering distinct gameplay styles. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4+ Difficulty levels to test your skills. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 Runes variants to upgrade and enhance your dice. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Potions to aid you in battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Omega upgrades to transform your runes into mighty forces.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Figure levels with rewards every step.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/90fc110459feb52bfd189baecd433421.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=300 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/90fc110459feb52bfd189baecd433421.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/a03b0749dbb616305719e5b996dbe9d5.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=530 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/a03b0749dbb616305719e5b996dbe9d5.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture through a medieval fantasy world, beautifully rendered in pixel art, music by Andrew Goodwin. Expand your <strong>collection</strong> by uncovering every prism, rune, and relic during runs. <strong>Challenge</strong> yourself and your friends by recording the highest attack, amassing the largest gold amount, or mastering your favorite prism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember your ultimate goal : to <strong>free Fortuna</strong>, unjustly imprisoned in Tartarus !</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/3391457710b23c54d4e98369a128ff86.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/3391457710b23c54d4e98369a128ff86.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/3391457710b23c54d4e98369a128ff86.mp4?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll Five is a dice-based <strong>roguelike</strong> deckbuilder that challenges you to master the art of <strong>dice rolling</strong> and deal shocking amount of <strong>damage</strong> to monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/1d35548f76dfee80c8e7c372f16d5ad3.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/1d35548f76dfee80c8e7c372f16d5ad3.webm?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/1d35548f76dfee80c8e7c372f16d5ad3.mp4?t=1744219426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/b0067554ade81fb083e5525bf1242aad.poster.avif?t=1744219426\" width=620 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971390/extras/b0067554ade8